      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The National Apple show, which\nproved a big success from every\nstandpoint except in a financial\nway, Will be held again next win\nter. This was the decision OF a\nJoint committee representing the\nchamber of commerce, the apple\nshow and the national irrigation\ncongress last night. The commit\ntee heartily favored the repetition\nof the show and declared it should\nbe made an annual event in Spo-\nkane. Ways and means will be\nfound to properly finance the I'M\ndertaking.\n\n\nThe joint committee also ar\nranged for the big irrigation con-\ngress and to advertise Spokane\nand the Inland empire extensively\nat the A-Y-P exposition."
    }
  ]
